msgid ""
"Proper DNS configuration (SPF, DKIM, DMARC) prevents your emails from "
"landing in spam folders and ensures recipients can verify your emails are "
"legitimate. This is essential for transactional emails like order "
"confirmations and password resets."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi DNS yang tepat (SPF, DKIM, DMARC) mencegah email Anda masuk ke "
"folder spam dan memastikan penerima dapat memverifikasi bahwa email Anda "
"sah. Ini sangat penting untuk email transaksional seperti konfirmasi pesanan "
"dan pengaturan ulang kata sandi."

