msgid ""
"DKIM adds a digital signature to your emails that receiving servers can "
"verify using a public key in your DNS records."
msgstr ""
"DKIM menambahkan tanda tangan digital ke email Anda yang dapat diverifikasi "
"oleh server penerima menggunakan kunci publik dalam catatan DNS Anda."

