msgid ""
"Proper DNS configuration is essential for email deliverability. Configure "
"SPF, DKIM, and DMARC records to ensure your emails reach recipients' inboxes "
"instead of spam folders."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi DNS yang tepat sangat penting untuk pengiriman email. "
"Konfigurasikan catatan SPF, DKIM, dan DMARC untuk memastikan email Anda "
"sampai ke kotak masuk penerima, bukan ke folder spam."

msgid "Why DNS Configuration Matters:"
msgstr "Mengapa Konfigurasi DNS Penting:"

msgid "Prevents spam filtering:"
msgstr "Mencegah penyaringan spam:"

msgid "ISPs verify your domain using SPF, DKIM, and DMARC"
msgstr "ISPs memverifikasi domain Anda menggunakan SPF, DKIM, dan DMARC"

msgid "Improves deliverability:"
msgstr "Meningkatkan pengiriman:"

